{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO59051B0907P0D1N000481", "chronotag": "1741212625866", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "CL481", "numeroOrdreDepot": "481", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CION_LOIS", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO59051B0907P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PIONANR5L17B0907", "triAmendement": "bqaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaf", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA610968", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845439", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"acteurRef": ["PA841701", "PA841351", "PA794022", "PA794778"]}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Amirshahi,  Mme&#160;Balage&#160;El&#160;Mariky, M.&#160;Duplessy, M.&#160;Iordanoff et Mme&#160;Regol"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 8 bis", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 8 BIS", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 8 BIS", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0907.asp#D_Article_8_bis"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Supprimer cet article.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Cet amendement vise la suppression de l&#x2019;article 8 bis, pre&#x0301;voyant d&#x2019;e&#x0301;tendre le de&#x0301;lai d&#x2019;application de l&#x2019;expe&#x0301;rimentation jusqu&#x2019;au 31 de&#x0301;cembre 2028 a&#x0300; son premier aline&#x0301;a, et de ne donner acce&#x0300;s au Premier ministre comme centralisateur, uniquement les correspondances et plus les informations et les documents.</p><p>La suppression de cet article intervient a&#x0300; deux titres. D&#x2019;abord, elle vise a&#x0300; supprimer la prolongation de l&#x2019;expe&#x0301;rimentation, disproportionne&#x0301;e au regard de la menace. Ensuite, elle vise a&#x0300; supprimer la disposition qui inte&#x0300;gre une re&#x0301;duction des pre&#x0301;rogatives du Premier ministre dans la consultation des informations et des documents recueillis, cre&#x0301;ant ainsi un flou sur la destination de ces informations et documents.</p><p>Le groupe E&#x0301;cologiste et Social alerte e&#x0301;galement sur le caracte&#x0300;re attentatoire aux liberte&#x0301;s individuelles de l&#x2019;article 8 bis.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2025-03-01", "datePublication": "2025-03-04", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Rejet\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2025-03-05T23:09:58+01:00", "sort": "Rejet\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO59051B0907P0D1N000481?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"idDiscussion": "75690", "typePosition": "Dernier"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}